data.description: Fantastic get away home w/ West Beach Water views nestled in cul-de-sac close to Swan Lake Park.  This home has two stories of windows from the main floor to roof. Primary bedroom & bath are on the main floor with laundry room adjacent to primary bath. Full sized kitchen on 2nd floor along with living room & dining area. Great 2nd story deck to view sunrises & sunsets. Property has short-term rental potential! Property needs some attention; bring your hammer & your beach home dreams to make it all yours! Detached two-car garage. Close to NAS Ault Field, shopping & 20!  Come and see for amazing water & mountain views!
